    (96,'B411','Biology of Marine Organisms','BIOL','UG',3,'University Of South Carolina Beaufort','(Prerequisites: BIOL B101, BIOL B102) Biological concepts emphasizing adaptation to marine environments. Laboratory experiments emphasize
