    (97,'B302','Cell and Molecular Biology','BIOL','UG',3,'University Of South Carolina Beaufort','(Prerequisite: a grade of ‘C’ or better BIOL B102) Principles of eukaryotic cell structure, molecular organization and physiology. Genome organization
