    (259,'B327','Design of Mechanical Elements','CSXE','UG',3,'University Of South Carolina Beaufort','(Prerequisite: CSXE B260.) Design against static failure and fatigue failure of structural members and machine parts; design and selection of components including fasteners, welds, shafts, springs, gears, bearings, and chain drives.'),
