    (331,'B101','Composition and Rhetoric','ENGL','UG',3,'University Of South Carolina Beaufort','An introduction to university-level writing, emphasizing the rhetorical approaches necessary to understand other writers'' purposes and stances, create effective writing, and develop processed for composing texts for academic, civic, professional, and personal purposes.'),
    (332,'B250','Copyediting and Document Design','ENGL','UG',3,'University Of South Carolina Beaufort','(Prerequisite: ENGL B102, with a grade of ''C'' or higher) This course gives students an overview of the skills necessary to prepare texts (in a range of
