    (524,'B250','Interdisciplinary Studies Internship','IDST','UG',3,'University Of South Carolina Beaufort','(Prerequisite: IDST Major or Minor only, IDST B297, or consent of instructor) Provides students with the opportunity to apply interdisciplinary research
