    (741,'B399','Independent Study in Psychology','PSYC','UG',3,'University Of South Carolina Beaufort','(Prerequisite: Contract approval is required, and PSYC B101 and consent of instructor) Closely supervised project or research experience in psychology. May be repeated for up to six credit hours. Not for psychology major credit.'),
