    (775,'B401','Health Care Delivery Systems','PUBH','UG',3,'University Of South Carolina Beaufort','{§ NURS B401} (Prerequisite: PUBH 310 or NURSB326 or RN Licensure or consent of the instructor.) Systems theory, health care delivery systems
